"Description": "Enables pioneer teleportation between two linked Portals.

Each Portal can only have a single link. 
A link can only be made between a Main and Satellite Portal.

A Fuel source needs to be supplied to the Main Portal which will be consumed to establish and maintain the Portal link.

WARNINGS:
- Massive power draw will occur during start-up. Power Storage recommended. 
- Link start-up will take time. Letting the connection expire is not recommended.
- Large power draw on use. Increases with travel distance.
- Failure to deliver sufficient Fuel will cause the link to expire.
- FICSIT does not condone the use of wormhole technology. Any usage of wormhole technology is at the user's own risk."
}